SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: Home delivery is available for standard and bulky items. In-store pickup is also an option. Parcel shop and parcel locker delivery are not mentioned.
PROVIDERS: Deliveries are handled by Overseas Express and IN-TIME.
PRICING: Standard shipping costs range from 5,04 € (up to 2kg) to 15,93 € (up to 50kg). Bulky item shipping costs range from 21,24 € (up to 100kg) to 55,74 € (up to 500kg). Shipping is free for orders over 50,00 €. Cash on delivery (COD) incurs a surcharge of 1,99 €.
DELIVERY TIME: The standard delivery timeframe is within 5 working days.
RESTRICTIONS & SPECIAL SERVICES: There is no information on express delivery, weekend delivery, or specific surcharges/restrictions for island deliveries. In-store pickup is available at their Zagreb and Osijek locations.
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: Shipping information is located within the 'Kako kupiti' (How to buy) page, not on a dedicated delivery page. The information provided is clear, especially the detailed weight-based pricing table, but it lacks details on common services like express, weekend, and island delivery.
